{"tid":1236252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一齊討論]經過今日陳醫生單野後 我覺得可以開多條媒體既戰線","createTime":"2019-06-17T11:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T07:36:45.000Z","uid":146887,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"835bb0608cbc84aa7c3bb0f1f60988f99948f8ac","tid":1236252,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"一單一單既新聞爆出黎 可能有部分既香港人已經麻木左<br />\n但我地絕對唔可以睇小呢幾日既新聞既威力！！<br />\n例如<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逃犯條例本身<br />\n黑警無預警開槍爆頭 係和平示威區放tear gas<br />\nHA交patient個人資料比黑警<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n以上幾單野 唔只係唔人道 甚至可以話係反人類既行為<br />\n加上香港係國際上有一定地位 背後管治個政府反而咁腐敗 兩件事之間既龐大反差 令到呢排既事更有新聞價值<br />\n隔離有巴打出公開信 清算港共政權<br />\n所以我覺得我地可以組織一班外文（唔只係英文）叻既巴絲 一齊做以下既野<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">篩選有價值既新聞<br />\n去信比cnn/ times等國際 唔同國家既media<br />\n係唔同地方 例如reddit/twitter等social media<br />\n諗標題 內文 開post吸attention</span><br />\n效法依家無領袖 無大台 集思廣益既社運模式去做文宣<br />\n兄弟爬山之餘 我地亦都應該係合適既時候齊心向前！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係前面衝既義士升級之餘 我地亦都應該將media呢一條線升級！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc002ff6044749420224e25aeb7de027e0c5c8b","tid":1236252,"uid":146887,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:31:48.000Z","msg":"一齊討論下點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再好似2014咁<br />\n拎住條同花順 之後再一隻一隻咁打出去<br />\n唔要階段性勝利 唔要分化！"},{"pid":"15cc025a073d31e9b5f335e4c1ab449c04361e53","tid":1236252,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:34:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>係時候好好地運用下外國勢力呢隻牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8dc6d66dfcf21b3ccb20fd1747087f86dc383111","tid":1236252,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e265f79eacbc1cffd976236f8cb745e491b28d49","tid":1236252,"uid":146887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:44:08.000Z","msg":"除左夠juicy既新聞<br />\n我地亦都需要有創意既巴打 去諗唔同<span style=\"color: red;\">聽落無咩可能 但中共統治下就會變成有可能既野</span> 同依家逃犯條例既概念拉埋一齊<br />\n例如&quot;病人資料庫+逃犯條例=器官uber&quot; 呢個idea咁<br />\n我地應該需要巴打將佢翻譯做英文 再用juicy啲既方法放上唔同平台<br />\n例如整meme咁 <br />\n盡可能咁放大條例既害處 先可以有效make noise<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd743dbfc002d50bc3bfb67104181df133e4390","tid":1236252,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"要推到比外國知道"},{"pid":"1b5582c245d88d585538b515ef5f9dd0d3988987","tid":1236252,"uid":129760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:45:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"507a2156da41fbf484a03783d9fb749a6f3d9b64","tid":1236252,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acd743dbfc002d50bc3bfb67104181df133e4390","tid":1236252,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"要推到比外國知道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:45:14.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊討論下應該要點做"},{"pid":"5c1a1cc2c87efbacb5fb8bd08ded0eaa045f1170","tid":1236252,"uid":104758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:46:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"964f6766b89017acff9cfbbf795e9f58ebe9abbf","tid":1236252,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:46:44.000Z","msg":"有無英文/外文叻既巴絲呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663745340b68b8494274a7